content: <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 8px;">﻿</span><span class="framer-text" style="-webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; font-size: 36px;" manrope="" placeholder",="" sans-serif;="" font-weight:="" 900;="" font-variation-settings:="" normal;="" color:="" rgb(56,="" 89,="" 166);="" font-size:="" 24px;="" text-align:="" start;="" text-transform:="" capitalize;="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""><b>The team behind everything<br></b></span></p><p style="margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; padding-bottom: 0.5em;"><font color="#000000" style=""><span style="font-family: Manrope, " manrope="" placeholder",="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 20px;="" text-align:="" justify;="" -webkit-text-fill-color:="" rgba(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""><b>At </b></span><span class="framer-text" style="-webkit-font-smoothing: inherit; font-family: Manrope, " manrope="" placeholder",="" sans-serif;="" font-weight:="" 700;="" font-variation-settings:="" normal;="" font-size:="" 20px;="" text-align:="" justify;="" -webkit-text-fill-color:="" rgba(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"=""><b>Kwizera Ch</b>arity Foundation</span><span style="font-family: Manrope, " manrope="" placeholder",="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 20px;="" text-align:="" justify;="" -webkit-text-fill-color:="" rgba(0,="" 0,="" 0);="" white-space-collapse:="" preserve;"="">, we are more than a team, we are a family united by a deep passion for change.
